{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 2018394, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Sellanor", "body": "Say #1 <Triggered upon accepting \"Lunatic Lieutenants\">: Bring those battleplans back to me and we can begin to dismantle this Iron Horde.\n\nSay #2 <Triggered upon accepting \"For Nethergarde!\">: Plant the Alliance flags inside Nethergarde, our men will do the rest.\n\nSay #3 <Triggered upon turn in \"Lunatic Lieutenants\">: Hmm... it appears the Iron Horde has formed an alliance with the Dreadmaul ogres. This is going to be more difficult than I thought.\n\nSay #4 <Triggered upon turn in \"For Nethergarde!\">: We must keep pushing back on the Iron Horde. They need to know we will not sit by and watch as they kill our brothers and sisters.\n\nSay #5 <Triggered upon accepting \"Gar'mak Bladetwist\">: I will meet you at Okril'lon. We will take down Gar'mak together.\n\nSay #6 <Triggered upon turn-in of \"Gar'mak Bladetwist\">: With Gar'mak dead the Iron Horde will be in disarray until they appoint a new leader here on Azeroth. Although we have won this battle, I fear the war has just begun.", "date": "2014-10-24T12:19:32-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2014-10-24T19:34:14-05:00", 3, "Sellanor"]}
