{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 781495, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "FarseerLolotea", "body": "S\r\nP\r\nO\r\nI\r\nL\r\nE\r\nR\r\n\r\nfor anyone who cares...\r\n\r\nAccording to the tie-in comic, Garona Halforcen is this guy's niece.", "date": "2009-07-18T02:03:55-05:00", "rating": 49, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "And therefor Great-uncle of Med'an", "creationdate": "2009-07-25T12:28:59-05:00", "id": 111736, "rating": 23, "commentid": 781495, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "205809", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "That is serious pedigree lines.", "creationdate": "2009-09-21T06:25:30-05:00", "id": 123247, "rating": 14, "commentid": 781495, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "272046", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "His sister was raped by one of Gul'dan's Orc underlings to sire Garona, who was then artificially aged and brain washed.  Maraad was the one who taught Garona's son, Med'an, how to use the Holy Light.", "creationdate": "2010-06-05T14:53:08-05:00", "id": 166770, "rating": 16, "commentid": 781495, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "LeviGratton", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
